"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-mike-tirico-peyton-manning-kelly-clarkson-olympic-opening-ceremony-paris-nbc\", \"text\": \"Mike Tirico will be joined by Peyton Manning and Kelly Clarkson to host live broadcast coverage of the Paris Olympic Opening Ceremony on July 26 on NBC and Peacock at noon Eastern time.  The trio made the announcement on \\\"The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon\\\" on Tuesday.  Tirico returns to host a fourth consecutive Opening Ceremony.  Manning, the Hall of Fame quarterback, and Clarkson, the Grammy-winning singer and TV personality, will make their Olympic broadcast debuts.  \\\"Today\\\" Show hosts Savannah Guthrie and Hoda Kotb will also be part of the broadcast team, stationed on a bridge along the route.  The Paris Opening Ceremony will be the first of its kind - held outside of a stadium on a nearly four-mile stretch along the Seine River in the heart of the French capital.  The Parade of Nations will be done with boats carrying athletes past landmarks, climaxing with the Eiffel Tower.  It's expected that a few hundred thousand spectators will be scattered along the route, including on at least one bridge over the river.  The ceremony starts at 7:30 p.m. local time, which is 1:30 p.m. Eastern time.  .@kellyclarkson, Peyton Manning and@miketiricowill be hosting the@NBCOlympicsopening ceremony!#FallonTonightpic.twitter.com/bz5FJMdHeq  \\ud83d\\uddd3 26-07-2024Paris, its river, its monuments, its quays...for an extraordinary show. Let us celebrate sport in the city!This is the Opening Ceremony of the#Paris2024Olympic Games!pic.twitter.com/xS2D2xGygG    A Division ofNBCUniversal.  DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site. This service is intended for adult audiences. No guarantees are made for any specific outcome. If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.  \\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\"}"